<L>__{exterior the abyss}
<A>__{bud is in an enormous school of bioluminescent squid, graceful, attenuated creatures less than a foot long. thousands of then glide in ghostly arcs around him, filling the black void as far as the eye can see. he stares at them in wonder. reaches out and touches one, catches it, lets it go. are they really here? he can no longer be sure of his own perceptions.}
